Package: tusk
Type: Package
Title: Conveniently access gridded climate data sets
Version: 0.8
Date: 2015-07-29
Author: Christian Zang
Maintainer: Christian Zang <christian.zang@wzw.tum.de>
Depends:
    ncdf4,
    raster,
    rgdal
Description: This small package aims at extracting point-specific climate data
    from some common gridded climate data sets, and allows to downscale to
    30 arc seconds using the Worldclim grid
License: GPL-3
